NAME

PerlIO::Util - A selection of general PerlIO utilities

SYNOPSIS

	use PerlIO::Util;

	# creates $file if needed, and calls flock(IN, LOCK_SH)
	open IN, '<:creat :flock', $file; 

INSTALLATION

	To install this module, run the following commands:

		perl Makefile.PL
		make
		make test
		make install


DEPENDENCIES

	perl 5.8.0 or later.


